EmaWelsh AM akhatsateka ngekubukeka njengemaMuppets.
Labanye bantfu bayabate kutsi i-AM ingaphindze ibe yi-MWP (Lilunga lePhalamende yase-Wales).
Loku kungaciniseki kubangelwe tinhlelo tekutsi leSigungu sibitwe ngekutsi yiPhalamende yaseWelsh.
Tinyenti tinhlangano tepolitiki letinelikhono lekukhuluma ngekutsi loku kutawusho kutsi kuncono yini kutsi kube khona umehluko.
Lomunye umcashwa we-AM watsi licembu lakhe likhatsatekile ngekutsi lesihloko "sifana ne-Twp ne-Pwp".
Kubo bonkhe labafundza ngaphandle kwe Wales: nge Welsh twp kusho silima kantsi pwp kusho umchamo.
Umuntfu lowakhuluma ne-AM watsi licembu lonkhe "liyatfukutsela" futsi liniketa letinye tindlela.
Umuntfu loligama lakhe lelingasiyo i-MVP, lohlala eWelsh, watsi "uyakhululeka" mayelana nekuguculwa kwelibito lakhe, kodvwa watsi lokuhlelwa ngu-MWP kuya kuMuppet kungukuhlukunyetwa lokuncane.
Kuloku, leligama lesiWelsh lifanana naleso sase Yorkshire lesitsi u.
LiKhomishane leSigungu, lelisungula umtsetfo wekuguculwa kweligama, latsi: "Kuncuma kwekugcina mayelana nekutsi yini lekumele yentiwe ngemalunga esiGungu kutawuba semahlombe awo".
Umtsetfo weHulumende waseWales wanga-2017 uniketa Sigungu saVelonkhe seWelsh emandla ekushintja ligama laso.
NgaJuni, lelikomidi lakhipha imiphumela yelucwaningo lolwentiwe kuletincomo, lokukhombise kutsi kunekwesekelwa lokukhulu kutsi leSigungu sibitwe ngekutsi yiPhalamende yase Welsh.
Mayelana nesihloko se-AM, leKhomishane yakhetsa i-WMP nobe lilunga lePhalamende lase-Welsh, kepha, inketho ye-MWP yatfola kwesekelwa lokukhulu ekubonisaneni nemphakatsi.
Ema-AMs aphakamisa letinye tindlela, kepha kulwa kwekufinyelela kuvumelana kungaba buhlungu enhloko ku-Elin Jones, sikhulu lesengamele, lokumele etfule umtsetfosisekelo wetingucuko emavikini lambalwa.
Lolucwaningo lutawuhlanganisa netingucuko letitsite endleleni yekusebenta kweSigungu, lokufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekungafaneleki kwe-AMs kanye nekwakheka kweluhlelo lwekukhetsa.
Uma i-AM icoca ngalomtsetfo, itawuncuma kutsi itawubitwa ngaliphi ligama.
