Kutamatama kwemhlaba, ema-tsunami e-Indonesia kubulala emakhulu, linani lebantfu labafile liyakhula
Ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami lokwabangela kutsi emagagasi lamakhulu ashaye emabhishi esihlengeni sase-Indonesia i-Sulawesi, lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa, labanyenti bagcwala, kusho tiphatsimandla ngeMgcibelo.
NgaLesihlanu, emakhulu ebantfu abehlangene emcimbini lobewusedvute nelwandle edolobheni lasePalu, ngesikhatsi emagagasi laphakeme ngemamitha langu-18 agudla lusentse, abulala bantfu labanyenti futsi abhubhisa konkhe lobekukhona endleleni.
Le-tsunami yalandzela kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.5.
"Ngesikhatsi kushubile tsunami itolo, bantfu bebatiphilisa elusentseni futsi abazange basuke masinyane, bagcine bafile", kusho Somlomo we-BNPB, inhlangano yetekuvikela tinhlekelele yase-Indonesia, Sudopo Purwo Nugroho, watjela betindzaba eJakarta.
"Lentfutfu yemhlaba ayizange ite yodvwa, yafaka ekhatsi timoto, emabhasikidi, tindlu, yashaya konkhe lokwakusemhlabatsini", kwasho Nugroho, achubeka atsi lemvula yemhlaba yahamba ngesivinini lesingaba ngemakhilomitha langu-800 elwandle ngaphambi kwekutsi ishaye elusentseni.
Watsi labanye bantfu bagibela etihlahleni kute baphephe ku-tsunami futsi baphila.
Bantfu labangu-16 700 batfunyelwe etindzaweni letingu-24 ePalu.
Titfombe tasemoyeni letikhishwe yi-Disaster Management Agency tikhombisa kutsi takhiwo letinyenti kanye netitolo tabhidlika, emabhuloho agobeka futsi abhidlika, futsi lisontfo laKhisimusi lavalwa ngemanti.
Ngisho nangemuva kwaloko, lelidolobha leliselugwini laphindze latsintseka kakhulu ngeMgcibelo.
Lokuzamazama kwemhlaba lokulandzelanako kwavakala endzaweni lenebantfu labatigidzi letingu-2.4.
I-Indonesia's Institution for Technology Assessment and Application (BPPT) yatsi emandla lakhokhwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu ngaLesihlanu abenemandla langetulu kwa-200 kunemandla elibhomu lemvelo lelahlwa eHiroshima eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Lencwadzi itsi, "Lendzawo lebeyikhona, lebeyisekugcineni kwegodzi lelidze, yenta kutsi kube nemtsunami lomkhulu".
Ngeroh, umonakalo uchazwa ngekutsi "ubukhulu", futsi tinkhulungwane tetindlu, tibhedlela, timakethe kanye nemahhotela kubhujisiwe.
Watsi kutfolakale imitimba yebantfu lababanjwe ngaphansi kwetakhiwo letiwile, watsi bantfu labangu-540 balimele kantsi labangu-29 basengakafi.
