JE: Emakhono elulwimi ayintfo lebalulekile kubantfu labahlala emhlabeni wonkhe.
Tikolwa letizimele taseScotland tigcina umlandvo wekuhlonishwa ngekuhlonishwa, futsi loku kuyachubeka naku-2018, kufaka ekhatsi lolunye luhlu lwemiphumela yekuhlola lengakavami, lekhokhwa kuphela ngemphumelelo yemuntfu ngamunye neyabanye kutemidlalo, tebuciko, temculo kanye naleminye imisebenti yemphakatsi.
Letikolwa, letinebafundzi labangetulu kwa-30 000 eScotland yonkhe, timelelwa nguMkhandlu Wetifundza Wetifundza (SCIS), lofuna kuniketa bafundzi babo nebatali babo tinsita letisezingeni lelisetulu.
Tikolwa letitimele tihlose kulungisa bafundzi bato kutsi batfole imfundvo lephakeme, umsebenti wabo labakhetsa kuwwenta kanye nendzawo yabo njengebahlali bemhlaba.
Njengendzawo yekufundza lengakhetsa nekusebentisa luhlelo lwekuhlela luhlelo lwetemfundvo, sibuka tilwimi tesimanje njengentfo letsandvwa kakhulu etikolweni.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, loko kutawuya engcondvweni yakhe.
Nangabe ukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, loko kutawuya enhlitiyweni yakhe.
Lokubaluleke kakhulu kutsi sikhumbule kutsi singeke setsembele esiNgisini sodvwa kute sakhe budlelwane nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngekubuka imiphumela yemiphumela yemathemu yakamuva, siyakubona kutsi tilwimi tihola emagameni ekufundza ngetemfundvo letinemaphuzu lasetulu ekuphumelela etikolweni letitsite.
Bafundzi labangu-68% labafundza tilwimi bangaphandle batfola ema-A lasetulu.
Lemininingwane lehlanganiswe etikolweni letingu-74 letitfolakalako te-SCIES ibonisa kutsi bafundzi labangu-72% batfola ema-A laphakeme ngesiMandarin, 72% batfola ema-A esiJalimane, 69% batfola ema-A esiFulentji, kantsi 63% batfola ema-A esiSpanishi.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letizimele eScotland tisekela tilwimi tangaphandle njengelwati lolubalulekile, lolutawufuneka kubantfwana nakubantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Lulwimi njengesifundvo sekukhetsa nyalo selucondziswa njengesifundvo setikolo letimele kanye netifundvo te STEM (Isayensi, teTheknoloji, teNgungcondvo kanye neTibalo) kuletinye tindzawo.
Lucwaningo lwe-UK Commission for Jobs and Skills lwanga-2014 lutfole kutsi kuncane emakhono elulwimi lokwenta 17 ekhulwini setizatfu letiniketiwe bacashi tekugcwalisa tikhala.
Ngako-ke, emakhono elulwimi aya ngekuba yimfuneko kulolusha kute alungiselele umsebenti walo.
Leti tingcweti tiyasebenta kulelive lelibuswa ngumhlaba wonkhe, futsi tiyasebenta nasetindzaweni lapho khona bantfu labanyenti bafuna lulwimi.
Kungakhatsaliseki kutsi bakhetsa umsebenti muni, nangabe bafundza lolunye lulwimi, bangazuza kakhulu ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi ngobe banemakhono latawubasita kuphila kwabo konkhe.
Ngenca yekwati kucoca nebantfu bakwamanye emave, umuntfu lowati tilwimi letinyenti utawuvele abe nguloholako kulomncintiswano.
Ngekusho kwelucwaningo lwe-YouGov lwanga-2013 lolwentiwe kubantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4 000 base-UK, bantfu labangu-75 ekhulwini bebangakhoni kukhuluma lulwimi lolungetiwe lolungasilo lulwimi lwabo, kantsi lulwimi lwesiFrench belukhulunywa bantfu labangu-15 ekhulwini kuphela.
Kungako-ke kubaluleka kwekusisa ekufundziseni tilwimi kubantfwana betfu.
