Kit Harrington, longumdlali lomkhulu we-Game of Thrones, uhlaselwe yindvodza lenesifo.
Kit Harrington watiwa kakhulu ngendzima yakhe njenge John Snow, umbulali wetinkemba ku HBO's violent medieval fantasy series Game of Thrones.
Kodvwa lomdlali loneminyaka lengu-31 budzala wagceka kutsi lelidvodza libonakala liyinhloko, watsi tindzima letinjalo tesikrini tivame kwenta bantfwana bacabange kutsi kufanele babe nemandla kute batfole ludvumo.
Akhuluma neSunday Times Culture, Kit watsi uyakholwa kutsi kukhona 'lokungahambi kahle' futsi ubuta kutsi singabhekana njani nenkinga yebulili lobunetitsako esikhatsini se #MeToo.
Kitt, losandza kushada naRose Leslie, 31, longumlingisi wakhe we-Game of Thrones, uyavuma kutsi 'unesifiso lesikhulu' sekulungisa lenkinga.
'Ngitiva nginemandla kakhulu nyalo - yini lephambene nebulima betfu?' washo njalo.
'Sifundzisani bantfwana betfu ngetinkinga lesibukene nato nyalo njengobe bakhula?'
Kit ukholelwa kutsi kubakhona kwebantfu labadvuna kakhulu kuthelevishini, kunguloko lokwenta kutsi kube nebudvodza lobunetitsako.
Wachubeka watsi: 'Yini lesiyitfola ngekutalwa, futsi yini lesiyifundziswa?
Yini leyenta bantfwana bacabange kutsi kufanele babe naletici letitsite kute babe ngemadvodza njengobe bafundziswa kuTV nasetitaladini?
Ngicabanga kutsi ngulomunye wemibuto lemikhulu yesikhatsi setfu - singakushintja njani?
Ngobe kukhona lokungakalungi ngalomntfwana.'
Kulengcoco wavuma kutsi angeke ente lokulandzelako nobe lokulandzelako ngemuva kwekuphela kwe-Game of Thrones ngeLisontfo lelitako, futsi 'ukhatsateke ngemasango emphi kanye nemahhashi.'
Kusukela ngaNovemba, Kit utawusebenta ekuvuseleleni i-True West yaSam Shepherd, indzaba yemkhiphi wemafilimu nemnakabo losigebengu.
Lomlingisi usandzile kuveta kutsi sipho semfati wakhe Rose ngiso lesimjabulisa kakhulu kuGame of Thrones.
'Njengobe ngahlangana nemkami kulomdlalo, wanginika umndeni wami lotako kanye nemphilo lelandzelako,' washo njalo.
Rose wadlala indzima yaGrit, umlingani waJohn Snow, umlingisi waKitt, kuloluhlelo lolunemlandvo lowatfola umklomelo we-Emmy.
