HIV/AIDS: EChina, kwenyuka kwebantfu labasandza kutfola ingculazi nga 14%
I-China imemetela kukhula lokungu-14% kwebantfu bayo labane-HIV ne-AIDS.
Tiphatsimandla tetemphilo titsi bantfu labangetulu kwa-820 000 kulelive sebanesifo.
Emaphesenti lacishe abe ngu-40,000 etinhlobo letinsha tekugula tivele ngekota yesibili ya-2018 kuphela.
Linyenti lalabantfu labasandza kutfolakele batfola lesifo ngekwelicansi, lokukhombisa kutsi besekwenteke lokunye.
Ngalokwetayelekile, i-HIV yayisakateka ngekushesha etindzaweni letitsite taseShayina ngekuniketa ingati lenengoti.
Kodvwa tikhulu tetemphilo taseShayina tatjela umhlangano lobewuse-Yunnan kutsi lesifo se-HIV sehlile kakhulu, sacishe saba lite.
Nobe kunjalo, linani lebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS eChina lenyuka ngeminyaka lengu-100 000.
Kutseleleka nge-HIV ngekwelicansi kuyinkinga lenkhulu emphakatsini we-LGBT waseShayina.
Kusukela nga-1997 bulili bebulili lobufanako bebungasiyo intfo lephulwa ngumtsetfo eChina, kodvwa lubandlululo lwe-LGBT lwachubeka nekukhula.
Lokutfolwe lucwaningo kukhombisa kutsi ngenca yemagugu lamasha alelive, cishe emadvodza langu-70 kuya ku-90 ekhulwini lalala nemadvodza agcine ashade nalabasikati.
Kungasebenti kahle kwaletindlela tekuchumana kwenta kutsi kube netindzaba letinyenti tekungenwa tifo.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende waseChina wetsembisa kutsi utawenta kutsi imitsi ye-HIV itfolakale emhlabeni wonkhe njengencenye yemitamo yekubukana nalesimo.
