Yini umkhosi webantfu labahlala emhlabeni wonkhe futsi kukhona yini lokwentiwe kute kucedvwe buphuya?
Umkhosi wemnyaka we Global Citizen Festival utawuba seNew York ngeMgcibelo lotako, utawuba netingwazi letinkhulu futsi umgomo walo utawuba ngulokufanako: kucedza buphuya emhlabeni wonkhe.
Kulomnyaka wesikhombisa we-Global Citizen Festival, tigidzi tebantfu titawube tihlangene e-Great Lawn yase Central Park, hhayi nje kute tijabulele buciko bebadlali labafana naJanet Jackson, Cardi B naSean Mendes, kepha kute tishumayele inhloso yalomkhosi - kucedza buphuya lobukhulu emhlabeni wonkhe nga-2030.
Umkhosi webahlali bemhlaba wonkhe, lowacala nga-2012, usungulwe yi-Global Poverty Project, licembu lelisebenta ngekubambisana nemhlaba wonkhe lelifuna kucedza buphuya ngekukhulisa sibalo sebantfu labakhutsata kucedza buphuya.
Kute utfole imvumo yekungena mahhala kulomcimbi (uma ungatsandzi kutsenga emakhadi e-VIP), babukeli bemcimbi bekufanele bente imisebenti letsite nobe "tento" letinyenti, njengekuvolontiya kusakata umgomo wabo wekucedza kubusa kwemhlaba, kutfumela ema-imeyili, kubita umholi wemhlaba nobe kwenta lokunye lokutsite lokuzuzisako.
Kodvwa-ke, yini lesingayenta kute sibe takhamuti temhlaba wonkhe nasesisele iminyaka lengu-12 kutsi sifinyelele umgomo wetfu?
Umbono wekubamba umkhosi wamahhala wemsindvo wekukhibika kutsi uyindlela lecotfo yekukhutsata bantfu kutsi batsatse sinyatselo, nobe ngulenye indlela yekukhetsa - lapho bantfu bacabanga kutsi kusayina sicelo nobe kutfumela i-tweet kuyintfo lenhle?
I-Global Citizen itsi inemibiko yekusebentisa "tento" letingetulu kwetigidzi letingu-19 kusukela nga-2011 letentiwa basekeli bayo ngetizatfu letehlukene.
Utsi tento takhe tisite ekucinisekiseni baholi bemhlaba kutsi batfumele imali lengetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-3 700 tetigidzigidzi temarandi kanye netinhlelo tetinhlelo letitawutsintsa bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-225 nga-2030.
Ekucaleni kwa-2018, lelicembu lakhipha tifungo letingu-390 kanye netimemetelo letivelako, lokungenani imali lengetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-R1 000 leyase iniketwe nobe yabutfwa.
Lelicembu lilinganisa kutsi imali lekhona seyivele itsintse imphilo yebantfu labacishe babe tigidzi letingu-649 emhlabeni wonkhe.
Letinye tetetsembiso letibalulekile tifaka ekhatsi i-Power of Nutrition. I-Power of Nutrition ibambisene ne-UK-based investors and organizers, "lesita bantfwana kutsi batfutfukise emakhono abo" futsi ngemuva kwekutfola ema-tweets langetulu kwa-4 700 lavela kubantfu emhlabeni wonkhe, yetsembisa kuxhasa lelive ngemali lengemadola latigidzi letingu-35 ekucedzeni kungondleki eRwanda.
Ngelusito lwahulumende wase UK, banikeli, bohulumende bemave kanye nebantfu labafana nani emhlabeni wonkhe, singenta kungalungi lokubangelwa kungondleki kube yintfo lengakabaluleki emlandvweni", kusho Tracey Ullman, sitfunywa se Power of Nutrition, etfula inkhulumo yakhe emcimbini we-Apreli 2018.
Lelicembu liphindze latsi ngemuva kwekwenta tinyatselo letingetulu kwa-5000 tekwenta ncono kudla kwemake nebantfwana e-UK, hulumende umemetele kutfola imali ye-Power of Nutrition Project, letawufinyelela bantfu labasikati nebantfwana labatigidzi letingu-5 ngetinsita tekudla.
Kulenye yetintfo letivame kubuta bantfu kulelikhasi, kuphendvula umbuto lotsi: "Yini lekwenta ucabange kutsi singakhona kucedza buphuya lobukhulu?"
Global Citizen watsi: "Lena itawuba yindlela lendze futsi lematima - ngaletinye tikhatsi sitawehlelwa tinhlekelele futsi sehluleke.
Kodvwa, njengetinyatselo tetfu tangaphambilini tekulwa nelubandlululo kanye nemalungelo eluntfu, sitawuchubeka siphumelele ngobe sibambisene futsi siyakhula.
