Umcondzisi we-US angalisebentisa libutho lemikhumbi laseMelika 'kuvimbela' kutsengiswa kwagezi eRussia - Interim Secretary
I-Washington Examiner itsi, i-US Secretary of State for International Affairs, Ryan Zinke, wachaza kutsi iWashington itawusebentisa umbutfo wemikhumbi "uma kunesidzingo" kuvimbela emandla aseRussia kutsi angafiki kuletinye timakethe, lokufaka ekhatsi iMiddle East.
Zink usola kutsi kutibandzakanya kweRussia eSyria - ikakhulukati lapho khona iRussia isebenta ngekumenywa nguhulumende wayo losemtsetfweni - kusento sekufuna timakethe letinsha temandla.
"BaseMiddle East ngobe ngifuna kutsi babe neligunya lekuniketa emandla agezi njengaseMpumalanga neYurophu, kanye naseNingizimu neYurophu", kusho Zinke.
Letiphatsimandla titsi, letindlela kanye nemathulusi ekubhekana naloku.
"Lelibutfo lemphi laseMelika linemandla ekuvikela kutsi emandla alo angafiki etimakethe, licinisekise kutsi tindlela taselwandle tivulekile, futsi licinisekise kutsi liyakwati kubamba uma kudzingeka.
Zinc Consumer Energy Alliance, licembu lelisebenta ngekubita "livi lebatsengi bemandla" eMelika, belikhuluma emhlanganweni.
Balinganisa tindzima taseWashington mayelana netintfo letenteka eRussia nase-Iran, baphindze batsi tifana ncamashi.
"Kuncishiswa kwemandla ekuphatsa kanye nekusetjentiswa kwalamanye emafutsa ngiko lokwenta kube melula kutsi i-Iran neRussia bakhone kutfola imali", kusho yena, abita iRussia ngekutsi "yimphuphu yinye" futsi atsi umnotfo waseRussia usekelwe kakhulu kumafutsa e-biobase.
Letitatimende tenteke ngesikhatsi hulumende waTrump etama kukhipha iRussia njengendlela lephephile kubatsengi baseYurophu ngekukhulisa kutsengiswa kwayo kwegesi yemvelo eYurophu.
Ngekulandzela loko, tikhulu te-Trump, kufaka ekhatsi Mengameli we-US Donald Trump, betama kwenta iJalimane kutsi iphume kuloluhlelo "lolubi" lwe-Nord Stream 2 pipeline, Trump lakusho kutsi "lutsatfwe" yi-Moscow.
I-Moscow iphindze yagcizelela kutsi i-Nord Stream 2 Pipeline Project letigidzigidzi leti-R1100 leyitawucitsa emandla ayo langetulu kwe-11,000 cubic metres, yintfo lephephile.
