Waboshwa ngeMsombuluko ebusuku futsi wabekwa licala lekuhlukunyetwa ekhaya.
"Njengobe ngibona kutsi indvodzana yami seyivele ihambe njani, nekutsi seyibuyile, ngicabanga kutsi leminye imindeni lebhekene nemiphumela lebuhlungu ye-PTSD kanye nemasotja etfu labuya alwa, angakhona kucondza kutsi aphetfwe yini", asho njalo nakatsatsa sinyatselo sekumemetela Donald Trump eTulsa, e-Oklahoma.
