Emave langu-18 D.C. asekela inchabhayi yenchubomgomo lensha yekukhosela.
Emave langu-18 kanye nesifundza sase-Columbia asekele incabho yetemtsetfo yemtsetfo lomusha waseMelika wekwala kusita bantfu lababalekile ekuhlukunyetweni ngemacembu ebantfu nobe ngekhatsi emakhaya.
Bameleli betifundza labangu-18 kanye neSigodzi sase-Columbia bafaka sicelo senkantolo eWashington ngaLesihlanu kute basekele umuntfu lofuna siphephelo lowalwa naloluhlelo, kubika i-NBC News.
Ligama leliphelele lemmangali e-Grace v. The American Civil Liberties Union, licala lelisemtsetfweni lelifakwe nga-Agasti lebeliphikisana nenchubomgomo yenhlangano, alishicilelwa.
Watsi waphatfwa kabi ngumlingani wakhe "kanye nebantfwana belicembu lakhe lelibudlova" kodvwa tiphatsimandla taseMelika tamlahla ngesicelo sakhe sekukhoseliswa ngaJulayi 20.
Abevalelwe ejele eTexas.
Bameli labamsekelako Grace bachaza i-El Salvador, iHonduras neGuatemala njengemave labhekene netinkinga tebudlova lobentiwa ngemacembu ebantfu kanye nebasemakhaya, lapho kunenombolo lenkhulu yebantfu labafuna kukhosela eMelika.
Umtsetfo lomusha waseMelika wekukhosela uvimbele sincumo lesatsatfwa liBhodi leTikhalo teBantfu labaFudukako nga-2014 lesasivumela bantfu lababalekile labangabhalisiwe lababalekele budlova basemakhaya kutsi bafake ticelo tekungena ekhaya lekuhlala.
Ummeli Jikelele weSifundza sase-Columbia, Carl Racine, washo emavi ngeLesihlanu atsi lenchubomgomo lensha "ingayinaki imitsetfo yeminyaka leminyenti yembuso, yelicembu kanye neyemave ngemave".
"Ngekwemtsetfo wesifundza, tonkhe ticelo tekutfola lusito kumele tibekwe ngekulandzela emaciniso netimo letikhona, futsi lokuvimbela kuphambene nemtsetfo", kusho umculu weNdvuna yeTemtsetfo.
Ngekusho kutsi bantfu labachamukile bavame kuba bacashi futsi "baniketa bantfu labasebenta ngetidzingo tabo", labameli baphindze batsi kungabikho lokubi ngemnotfo waseMelika ngekulahla bantfu labachamukile.
Ummeli Jikelele Jeff Sessions wayala lijaji leliphatselene netakhamuti kutsi lingasavumeli kutsi bantfu labahlukunyetiwe lababalekela budlova basekhaya kanye nebugebengu lobentiwa ngemacembu etfu kutsi bangene etindlini tabo.
"Siphephelo lesihle kulabo labaphuma eveni labo ngenca yekwesaba nobe kuhlushwa ngenca yekuhlonipha inkholo, inkholo, buve nobe lilunga lelicembu lelitsite letenhlalo nobe imibono yetembusave", kusho Sessions, embikweni wakhe ngaJuni 11, mayelana nalomgomo.
Tinkinga bantfu lababhekana nato onkhe malanga emhlabeni wonkhe - ngisho netinkinga letimatima kakhulu - akukaze kulindzeleke kutsi ticatululwe etindlini tekuhlala.
Njengobe linani lebantfu labafa liphindzeka kabili njengobe bantfu labaphilako batfolakala, bantfu labanyenti bayasindza.
Simo besisibi kakhulu kulabo labebasaphila.
"Ngiva ngicindzetelekile", kusho Risa Kusuma longumake loneminyaka lengu-35 budzala, lowagone umntfwana wakhe lobekanemkhuhlane endzaweni yekukhosela edolobheni lelibhujisiwe lasePalu.
"Kufike sitfo semphilo sinye njalo ngemzuzu.
Kunesidzingo semanti lahlobile".
Bantfu bakhona babonakala bakha timphahla tabo letinetintfo letinemanti, betama kusindzisa nobe yini lebebayitfola, babuyela emakhaya abo labhubhisiwe.
Bantfu labanyenti balimala futsi tibhedlela tatigcwele ngenca yekutamatama kwemhlaba lokungu-7.5.
Labanye balabo labalimele, lokufaka ekhatsi labaphukile emgogodleni nasemahlombe, bebakhashane neSibhedlela Selibutfo ePalu, lapho khona labagulako bebelashwa ngaphandle ngenca yekushaywa kakhulu.
Watsi nakacabanga ngekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwahlasela likamelo lakhe lelisesitezi sesihlanu ehhotela lapho bekahlala khona nemkakhe kanye nendvodzakati yakhe, wakhala tinyembeti.
