Ngemuva kweliviki linye liphephandaba lelisemtsetfweni laseChina likhiphe sikhangiso semakhasi lamane ephephandzabeni laseMelika lelikhuluma ngekuhlanganyela lokuzuzisako kwebhizinisi yaseMelika neChina, lichaza kutsi ummeli waseMelika eChina usebentise emaphephandzaba aseMelika kute asakaze inkhulumo-mphikiswano ngeBeijing.
Ngemuva kwekumangalelwa kwaMengameli weMelika Donald Trump ngaLwesitsatfu kutsi iChina ibambe luhlangotsi elukhetfweni lwe-US Congress ngaNovemba 6, lokwaphikiswa yiChina - liphephandaba lelisetjentiswa kakhulu e-Iowa - ngekucaphuna kuniketwa kwemali kweliphephandzaba lase China lelisuka ku-Des Moines Register.
Kusolwa kwaTrump ngekutsi iChina yetama kungenela lukhetfo lwaseMelika kusehluko lesisha emkhankasweni waseWashington wekucindzetela iChina, njengobe tiphatsimandla taseMelika titjele iReuters.
Nanobe kuvamile kutsi bohulumende bangaphandle bakhangise kute bakhutsate kutsengiselana, imphi yekuhwebelana emkhatsini weBeijing neWashington iyachubeka futsi kubonakala shengatsi iletsa umtselo lomkhulu kumikhicito yabo.
Tati tase China netase Melika titsi lemitselo yekubuyisa leyashiwo yi China ekucaleni kwemphi yekuhwebelana yayihloselwe kutsintsa batsengisi betimphahla letiphuma emaveni lafana ne Iowa, lasekela licembu la Trump le Republican.
Terry Branstad, longumbusi wesikhatsi lesidze wase Iowa, lowenta tintfo letinyenti tekulima eChina, watsi iBeijing ilimaze tisebenti, balimi kanye nemabhizinisi aseMelika.
Abhala sihloko ku-Des Moines Register yangeLisontfo, Branstad wabhala: "Bantfu baseChina nyalo sebayatiphakamisa ngekusebentisa titfunywa tepolitiki kute basite bantfu labakhululeke".
"Kute basakaze inkhulumo yabo, hulumende waseChina usebentisa emasiko aseMelika ekukhuluma ngenkhululeko kanye ne-journalism lelungile ngekutsi abeke tikhangiso letibhadalwako eDes Moines", kubhala Branstad.
"Ngalokwehlukile, emaphephandzaba latsengiswa etitaladini taseBeijing anetindzaba letimatima futsi awabonisi kahle imibono leyehlukene yebantfu baseChina mayelana nekuhlupheka kwemnotfo waseChina, ngobe betindzaba balawulwa kakhulu yi-CPC", kubhala yena.
