Michelsen wancoba imidlalo le-18, walahlekelwa ngu-20, futsi wadlala ema-draw lasikhombisa, Furyek watsi kuba khona kwakhe kwaletsa kubaluleka lokungakabonakali ecenjini.
"Uyahlekisa, uyasola, uyahlekisa, utsandza kuhlekisa bantfu futsi ungulomunye webantfu labakahle kutsi babe khona ecenjini", kuchaza yena.
"Badlali labasha batawujabula naye, futsi kutawuba mnandzi kubona loku kuleliviki.
Akagcini nje ngekudlala, kodvwa usiniketa lokunyenti".
Thomas Bourne, umphatsi wemave aseYurophu, bekati kutsi umbutfo lomkhulu utawushabalala masinyane.
Umcondzisi wase Europe, Thomas Bourne, wati kahle kutsi kuhola lokwenele ngaphambi kwemidlalo ye Ryder Cup yekugcina kungashintja kube luhambo lolungakalungi.
Dan wenta umchudzelwano wakhe wekucala ngemnyaka wa 1997 eValderrama, ngesikhatsi licembu lebeliholwa nguSev Ballesteros lihola emaMelika ngemaphuzu lasihlanu, kepha ngesikhatsi sekuphela kwemidlalo, bebakhatsatekile futsi bancoba ngemalengiso lophansi kakhulu wa 141⁄2-131⁄2 kuphela.
"Uticinisekisa kutsi sinemaphuzu lamakhulu e-Valderrama; sinemaphuzu lamakhulu eBrooklyn, lapho silahlekelwe khona, futsi siwine e-Valderrama, kepha ngesilinganiso lesincane", kusho Bourne ngesikhatsi abuka inhlolovo yekuncoba nga-5-3 ngaLesihlanu nangoLesibili nga-2018 lokwenta kutsi kube ne-10-6 ku-Lee Golf National.
Umlandvo utawungikhombisa kanye naloyo naloyo lolapha kulelicembu kutsi loku akusiko kuphela.
Kusasa kutawudzingeka kutsi nibhidlite yonkhe indzawo.
Hamba uye lapho futsi wente konkhe lokuhle.
Akukapheli uze ufinyelele emaphuzu akho ebhodini.
Umgomo wetfu kutfola lomudlalo futsi ngiko lesitawugxila kuko.
Ngikhulume ngako konkhe, ngigcile kubadlali labangu-12 labaseluhlangotsini lwetfu, kodvwa siyati kutsi ngubani loseluhlangotsini lwetfu lolunye - badlali labakhulu emhlabeni".
Born uyajabula ngekubonisa kwebadlali bakhe indzawo lematima, utsi: "Angeke ngikhone kuhamba embili.
Inselele yakusasa yehlukile.
Kusasa kutawuba nembukiso lotawubonakala, futsi kwenta loko kuhlukile.
Kuhle kudlala nemuntfu loshade naye nangabe tintfo tihamba kahle, kodvwa nawuhamba wedvwa, kuba matima kakhulu kuwe njengemdlali wegalofu.
Lona ngumlayeto lokufanele uwendlulisele kubadlali bakho kutsi batawenta konkhe lokusemandleni abo kusasa.
Nyalo, ushiya umuntfu loshade naye ngemuva futsi ufuna kutsi naye ente lokuncono kakhulu".
Ngalokwehlukile ku Bourne, Furyc lowalwa naye bekagcizelela kutsi badlali bakhe bente kahle kunebalingani babo, ngaphandle kwaRordon Speeth naJustin Thomas labahola emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulamane.
Furyc yena wente "umangaliso welilanga" eYurophu, ngaphambi kwekulahlekelwa, waba yincenye yelicembu lelaliphumelele emaceleni omabili aloluhlelo lolukhulu lwekugcina.
Nga-1999 ngesikhatsi indvuna Crenshaw ibuta badlali bakhe kutsi bebenta njani ngelilanga lekugcina, watsi: "Ngikhumbula onkhe emagama".
"Kusasa sinemidlalo le-12 lebalulekile, kodvwa kufanele sicale ngekushesha njengobe senibonile eBrooklyn, njengobe senibonile eMedina.
Nangabe isesha ngendlela yinye, ingasusa umfutfo lomkhulu emkhatsini.
Sitawubeka luhlu lwetfu loluhambisana naloko futsi sibeke badlali betfu endzaweni lesingacabanga kutsi sitawenta umlingo ngayo kusasa".
Thomas watfunyelwa phambili kute atame kulwa futsi wahlangana na Rory McIlroy emdlalweni loyinhloko, walandzelwa ngu Paul Casey, Justin Rose, John Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood, labanye base Europe lababephasi kwengcikitsi.
"Ngibeke labadlali kuloluhlu ngobe bengicabanga kutsi batawukhombisa tonkhe tinhlangotsi", kusho Bourne nakakhuluma ngetintfo latikhetsile.
Umkhumbi lomusha waseJalimane waphindze wahlehliswa
I-German Navy's latest warship, i-German Navy's latest warship, bekufanele kutsi isebente nga-2014 kutsi itsatse sikhundla semikhumbi yemphi yasemphini yasekupheleni Kwemphi Lemfisha, kepha ngenca yetinkinga tetinhlelo kanye netindleko letisetulu angeke ifike, lokungenani kuze kube ngumnyaka lotako, kusho imisakato yasendzaweni.
I-Die Zeit icaphuna sikhulumi semabutfo kutsi, kusebenta kwe "Rhyland-Fage", umkhumbi lomkhulu we-Baden-Württemberg-class, sekucinisekiswe kutsi utawusebenta kuletinye tinyanga tekucala temnyaka wa-2019.
Lomkhumbi bekufanele ufike emkhosini ngemnyaka wa 2014, kepha tinkinga letibuhlungu ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa kwato, tivimbele kutsi lomklamo lomkhulu ungaphumeleli.
Letine letitintfo letincane te-Baden-Württemberg-class leticeliwe ngemnyaka wa-2007 titotfwala tikhali letincane te-Bremen-class.
Kucatjangwa kutsi kutawuba nemabutfo lanemandla, ema-anti-aircraft squad kanye nemishini yekulwa nemikhumbi, kanye netintfo letingabonakali njengeradar, infrared kanye nemasignature e-acoustic.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile tifaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekugcina - lemikhumbi yekulwa lensha kumele ikwati kusetjentiswa khashane nemahhovisi emakhaya iminyaka lemibili.
Nanobe kunjalo, kubambezeleka lokukhulu kusho kutsi lemikhumbi yemphi yesimanje - lebeyingavumela iJalimane kutsi ikhombise emandla ayo elwandle - beyitawube seyiphelelwe sikhatsi uma seyicala kusebenta, kubika i-Die Zeit.
Lolu hlelo lwekulwa lwe F125 lwavela embikwebantfu ngemnyaka lophelile, ngesikhatsi tiphatsimandla tasemantini aseJalimane tingavumi kutsi lomkhumbi usetjentiswe futsi bawuphindzisela emkhombeni wemikhumbi iLom & Foss eHamburg.
Bekukwekucala kutsi umkhumbi ubuyiselwe kulenkampani yekwakha umkhumbi ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa.
Kute lokunyenti lokwatiswa ngetizatfu tekubuyiselwa emuva, kepha imisakato yaseJalimane yatsi kunetinkinga letinyenti "te-software kanye netintfo letitsite letitsite letitsite" letenta kutsi lomkhumbi ungakhoni kusebenta emkhankasweni wemphi.
Tinkinga letitsite letitsite betibalulekile, ngobe umkhumbi weBaden-Württemberg-class utawusetjentiswa ngemadvodza langu-120 - cishe kuhhafu wemandla ebantfu labakhona kuletingwenya letindzala te-Bremen.
Kantsi futsi, kwabonakala kutsi lomkhumbi unesisindvo lesidze kakhulu, lokwenta kutsi ungasebenti kahle futsi angeke ukhone kutfutfukiswa ngulelibutfo esikhatsini lesitako.
Le "Rhyland-Phage" lenemathani langu-7 000 ikhokha sisindvo lesiphindvwe kabili kunesicumbi semikhumbi lefanako lebeyisetjentiswa yiJalimane eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Ngetulu kwe-hardware lephukile, tindleko talomklamo wonkhe - kufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti - nako kwaba yinkinga.
Kusukela ekucaleni kwa-€2.2 billion - kuya ku-€3.1 billion ($3.6 billion) - lokumangalisako.
Tinkinga letisandza kuvela emikhombeni yemphi tibonakala tibaluleke kakhulu ngenca yekubaluleka kwemandla emikhumbi yemikhumbi yaseJalimane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, inhloko yelikomidi lekuvikela lephalamende yaseJalimane, wavuma kutsi libutfo lemikhumbi "lisaphelelwa ngemikhumbi lekhona kutsi lingasetjentiswa".
Lesikhulu satsi lenkinga ikhula ngekushesha njengobe sikhatsi sichubeka ngobe imikhumbi lendzala ayisebenti, kepha imikhumbi lemisha ayizange ifike.
Waphindze wadzabuka ngekutsi kute nobe yinye yetikebhe temphi te-Baden-Württemberg-class leyakhona kungena emkhunjini wemikhumbi.
Umndeni we-National Trust weva ngemfihlo ngemphilo yemalulwane
Lucwaningo lolusha lentiwa etintsabeni taseScotland lwembule kutsi bomgundvwane bayisebentisa njani indzawo lesetulu kute batfole kudla.
Kuyasekelwa kutsi lolucwaningo lusha lutawukhanyisa indlela letigogo letihamba ngayo futsi lusite ekucondziseni umsebenti wetekuvikela esikhatsini lesitako.
Lucwaningo lwebacwaningi base National Trust yase Scotland lutawulandzela imikhondvo yemabhungane lasemkhatsini kanye ne Soprano pipistrelles kanye nemikhondvo lemidze lemnyama kanye ne Dobbenton batsatse umgwaco wabo e-Inverieve Gardens lese West Ross.
Tinsimbi tekulalela letitsite titawufakwa etindzaweni letibalulekile kuleto tintfo tekulalela kute kulandzelwe umsebenti wemabhungane ngesikhatsi sonkhe semnyaka.
Basebenti be-NHS kanye netisebenti tekutivikela batawuphindze benta luhlolo lolusendleleni basebentisa titfo temtimba tangasese.
Bacwaningi bemisindvo yabo bonkhe bantfu batawuncuma kutsi yini leyenta kutsi emalulwane abite futsi batawuncuma nekutsi ngutiphi tilwane letibukako.
Lemephu yendzawo yekuhlala yemvelo kanye nembiko utawubese uyakhiwa kute kutfolakale sitfombe lesiphelele sekutiphatsa kwato ezingeni lemhlaba.
Rob Dever, umeluleki we-NTS we-Nature Conservation, wetsemba kutsi imiphumela itawukhombisa kutsi nguyiphi indzawo yemvelo lebalulekile kubologwaja nekutsi tilwane letitsite tiyisebentisa njani.
Lolwati lutawusita ekuchazeni tinzuzo temisebenti yekuphatsa tindzawo tendalo, njengekwakhiwa kwemihlambi kanye nekugcinwa kahle kwemhlaba wetihlahla wetichwaga kanye naletinye tinhlobo letihlobene nato.
Eminyakeni lelikhulu leyendlulile, linani lemikhomo eScotland nase-UK lehle kakhulu.
Tisetingotini tekulahlekelwa yindzawo yato kanye nendzawo yato yemvelo ngenca yekwakhiwa kanye nemisebenti yekutfutfukisa.
Kuphehlwa kwemandla emoya kanye nekukhanyisa nako kuyingoti, kanjalo netintfo letiphatselene nemakhemikhali etincwadzini tekubhala kanye netintfo tekwakha, kanye nekuhlaselwa ngemakati.
Emabhungane akaboni mbamba.
Nanobe kunjalo, indlela yabo yekuzingela ebusuku ibavumela kutsi babe netindlebe letisebenta kancono kunemehlo abo.
Basebentisa indlela yekucondzisa indzawo lenhle kute batfole tilwanyana kanye netintfo letingabavimbela.
I-NTS, lebhekele kunakekela takhiwo temlandvo letingu-270, tibhakabhaka letibalulekile letingu-38 kanye nemhlaba longemahekitha langu-76,000, itsatsa timphungane ngekucophelela lokukhulu.
Leti tinemalunga lalishumi laceceshiwe latawuhlola njalo, ahlole tindzawo tekuhlala futsi ngalesinye sikhatsi ente nemisebenti yekusindzisa.
Leligatja lasungula indzawo yekuvikela imfishi lemhlophe yekucala yaseScotland futsi leyatiwako eDumphries naseGalloway, lapho kuhlala khona tilwane letingu-8 kuletilishumi taseScotland.
David Thompson, longumphatsi walendzawo, watsi lendzawo beyingumkhakha lofanele.
Watsi: "Treeve yindzawo lenhle kakhulu yekuhlala bomantongomane".
"Sinebantfu labadzala, netihlahla letindzala, netindzawo letinhle.
Kodvwa kunalokunyenti lokusamangalisako ngemalulwane, ngako umsebenti lesitawukwenta lapha nakuletinye tindzawo utasisita sicondze kabanti ngaloko lokudzingekako kute aphile".
Ugcizelela sidzingo sekuhlola emalulwane ngaphambi kwekunakekela imphahla ngobe kungenta kutsi indzawo yekuhlala bomake labodvwa ingabi nelwati, lokuholela ekufeni kwalabasikati nebantfwana labangu-400, futsi kungafaka ingoti yekubhujiswa kwemmango wonkhe.
Emalulwane avikelekile futsi kubulala, kuhlukubeta nobe kuhlukubeta noma kubulala indzawo yawo yekuhlala kulicala lelisemtsetfweni.
Elizabeth Farrell, umphatsi waseScotland weLigwababa Conservation Trust, wakhutsata bantfu kutsi basite.
Watsi: "Kunalokunyenti lokudzingeka sikufundze ngemalulwane etfu ngobe asati kutsi simo semiphakatsi yetinhlobo letinyenti temalulwane asitsini".
Ronaldo waphika kutsi abetfuke, futsi bammeli bakhe balungiselela kutsi babeke licala lakhe kumagazini waseJalimane.
Cristiano Ronaldo wachaza kutsi emacala ekudlwengula labekwe wona "tingumlandvo longemanga" futsi watsi bantfu "bafuna kuwatsatsa njengendzaba lemanga" basebentisa ligama lakhe.
Bameli bakhe balungiselela kutsi licala lakhe liletfwe kumagazini waseJalimane lokutsiwa yi-Der Spiegel, lowakhipha letinsolo.
Umdlali wePortugal neJuventus, Catherine Mayorga, ngumuntfu wesifazane waseMelika lobekwe licala lekudlwengula lomunye umfati wakhe ehhotela laseLas Vegas nga-2009.
Der Spiegel ibike ngaLesihlanu kutsi imnike imali lengu-$375,000 kutsi angasho lutfo ngalendzaba.
Akhuluma nebalandzeli bakhe labatigidzi leti-142 nge-Instagram Live video ngemuva kwema-awa lambalwa umbiko walombiko, Ronaldo, loneminyaka lengu-33 budzala, wacabanga kutsi lombiko "ungumbiko longemanga".
"Cha, cha, cha, cha, cha.
Loko lakusho lamuhla kungumbiko longemanga", kusho umncobi we-Ballon d'Or emahlandla lasihlanu, akhuluma embikwekhamera.
"Bafuna kutenta bantfu babe ngemadvodza, futsi loko bakwenta ngenca yelibito lami.
Kuvamile loko.
Batama kutfola ludvumo ngelibito lami, kodvwa loko kuyincenye yemsebenti.
Ngingumuntfu lojabulako futsi konkhe kuhamba kahle", wachubeka ahleka.
Bameli baRonaldo balungiselela kumangalela Der Spiegel ngetinsolo, i-Reuters itsi "kukhuluma lokungemukeleki ngekungabata kwemkhakha wangasese".
Ummeli Christine Schertz watsi badlali "bangaticela sincephetelo lesihambelana nekwephulwa kwemtsetfo, lokungulenye yetintfo letimbi kakhulu letiphatselene nekuhlukunyetwa kwemalungelo eluntfu esikhatsini lesengcile".
Loku lokushiwo ngulomuntfu kwenteka ngaJuni 2009 endlini lencane lesePalm Hotel and Casino eLas Vegas.
Ngekusho kwemiculu leyetfulwe enkantolo yesifundza sase Clark County eNevada, ngemuva kwekuhlangana ku-nightclub, Ronaldo naMyorga batsi babuyela ekamelweni lemdlali, lapho amdlwengula khona.
Mayorga watsi ngemuva kwesehlakalo lesatfolakala, Ronaldo waguca phansi wamtjela kutsi "99%" ungumuntfu "lomuhle" futsi "1%" wamdvumata.
Lemiculu itsi Ronaldo wavuma kutsi utawuya ecasini naye, kodvwa watsi bekungasiko kwakhe.
Mayorga waphindze watsi waya emaphoyiseni futsi bekanetitfombe temilondza yakhe leyatsatfwa esibhedlela, kodvwa ngemuva kwaloko wavuma kutfola sivumelwano ngaphandle kwenkantolo ngobe bekesaba "kuphindzisela" futsi bekesaba "kuhlazeka embikwebantfu".
Mayorga, loneminyaka lengu-34, utsi nyalo sewubambezele kucedza ngobe usatfukutsele ngenca yaloko lokwenteka.
Ronaldo bekalungela kujoyina iReal Madrid esuka eManchester United ngesikhatsi kuhlaselwa, futsi waya e-Italy Giants Juve kuleliviki lelikhulu ngemali letigidzi leti-€100.
I-Brexit: I-UK itawuhlale 'iyatisola' ngekulahla bakhiciti bayo
Greg Clark, longunobhala wetekuhweba, watsi "kutawuhlala kunetinkinga" uma i-UK ingakhoni kuba ngumholi wemhlaba wonkhe wekukhicita timoto ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Wachubeka watsi "lokukhatsatako" kutsi i-Toyota UK itjele i-BBC kutsi itawumisa kwesikhashana umkhicito embonini yayo eBurnston ngaseDerby uma i-UK iphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwekwenta sivumelwano.
"Sidzinga sivumelwano", kwasho Mnu. Clark.
Umkhicito wemoto waseJapan utsi kubamnyama kwemisebenti kungenta kube nekubambezeleka emnceleni uma ngabe i-Brexit ingekho.
Sikhungo saseBurnston - lapho kwakhiwa khona ema-Auris ne-Avancis aseToyota - sakhicita cishe timoto letingu-1,50,000 emnyakeni lowengcile, futsi letingetulu kwa-90 ekhulwini tato tatfunyelwa kulamanye emave ase-Europe.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ekupheleni kwaMashi, sitawuva kukhicitwa kwetimphahla embonini yetfu", kusho Marvin Cook, longumphatsi we-Toyota eBurnston.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto base-UK, lokufaka ekhatsi i-Honda, i-BMW ne-Jaguar Land Rover, bakhuluma ngekukhatsateka ngekutsi kutawuba njani kutsengiselana lokuchamuka emnceleni nangabe i-EU iphuma ngaphandle kwesivumelwano.
Sibonelo, iBMW itsi itawuvala siteshi sayo lesincane e-Oxford ngemuva kwenyanga i-Brexit iphelile.
Lokukhatsateka lokukhulu kwetinkampani tekwakha timoto kutsi i-Brexit lengenabo batsengisi itawubeka umnotfo wato engotini.
Umklamo weToyota usebenta ngendlela "lesemtsetfweni" lapho khona tincenye tekukhicita titfolakala njalo ngemizuzu lengu-37 kubatsengisi base-UK nase-EU kute bakhicite timoto letitsite.
Uma i-UK iphuma e-EU ingakashayi mhlaka 29 Mashi, kungahle kube nekungahlaliseki emnceleni, futsi imboni itsi kungahle kube nekubambezeleka kanye nekushoda kwetindzawo tekusebenta.
Kutawusebenta kutsi iToyota ingafaki tintfo letitsite emapulazini ayo aseDerbyshire sikhatsi lesidze kunalolo lusuku, futsi inkampani itsi loko kutawuholela ekutseni ikhicite.
UMnumzane Clark watsi luhlelo lwa Theresa May lwekuba nebudlelwane lobuhle ne EU luhlelwe kahle kute kugwenywe kuhlolwa kwemincele.
"Sifuna sivumelwano lesincono kakhulu, njengobe ngishito, asisitsandzi nje kutsi siphumelele, kepha kufanele sijabulele lelitfuba", washo kulenhlelo ya-BBC4 namuhla.
Loku kufakazelwa hhayi yiToyota kuphela, kepha nalabanye bakhiciti, labadzinga kutsi sigcine loku kuliciniso, kute umchele wetekuphakela uhlale uphumelele.
Toyota ayizange ikwati kutsi kutawuphela sikhatsi lesingakanani kukhicitwa, kodvwa ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, yacaphela kutsi kukhuphuka kwetindleko kutawucedza kuchudzelana kwalemboni futsi kutawuphindze kutsintse nemisebenti.
Peter Suvlaris, lowasebenta eBurnstone iminyaka lengu-24 futsi loyinhlangano yetisebenti letisebenta kulelipulazi, watsi emalunga ayo akhatsateke kakhulu: "Kwetifundvo tami, uma sebaphelelwe ngumsebenti, angeke baphindze babuye".
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: 'Sibeke luhlelo lolucondzile nalolucinile lwebudlelwane betfu ne-EU.'
I-White House yatsi umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahle uchubeke.
Umhlangano waDonald Trump neSekela laMmeli Jikelele Rod Rosenstein, ungahle uhlehliswe liviki linye ngenca yekuphikisana lokukhona mayelana nalomuntfu lotawukhetfwa yiNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh, kusho iWhite House ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein wengamela umsebenti weMeluleki Lomkhulu Robert Mueller, lofaka ekhatsi kuphenya ngekungenelela kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwane emkhatsini waTrump nebangani bakhe kanye neRussia kanye nekungenelela kwemtsetfo lokungaba khona ngemengameli.
Sekuphele tinyanga letinyenti kucace eWashington kutsi Trump utawukhombisa liSekela laMmeli Jikelele indlela yekuphuma, futsi loko kungafaka inkhululeko yaMueller engotini.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, i-New York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein wabeka ucingo kute abhale inkhulumo naTrump, lebeyingaba nemiphumela yekususa Mengameli ngekusebentisa luCwebu lwema-25 lwekuChitjiyelwa kweMtsetfosisekelo.
Rosenstein wayiphikisa lendzaba.
Kodvwa ngeMsombuluko lowengcile waya eWhite House futsi bekukhulunywa ngekushiya kwakhe sikhundla.
Esikhundleni saloko, umhlangano weLesihlanu wamenyetelwa naTrump, lobekahlala e-United Nations eNew York ngaleso sikhatsi.
Trump watsi bekangeke akujabulele kukhipha Rosenstein, kepha lomhlangano wachutjwa kute agweme kuhlangabetana neLikomidi Leliphetse Temtsetfo laseSenate, lebelitawufakaza ngaKwano nalomunye walabasikati labambeka licala, Dokotela Christine Blasey Ford.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wayala luhlolo lwe-FBI lweliviki lonkhe lwekuphenya ngetinsolo letentiwa nguKwanu, lokwenta kutsi kuvotelwa kweSigungu Savelonkhe kwandze.
Sarah Sanders, sikhulu saTrump sekubika, wavela ku-Fox News Sunday.
Ngesikhatsi abuta mayelana nemhlangano waRosenstein, watsi: "Asikho sikhatsi lesibekiwe, kungenteka kutsi kutawuba kuleliviki, ngicabanga kutsi kungahle kuhlehliswe liviki linye ngenca yetintfo letichubekako neNkantolo lePhakeme".
Kodvwa, siyabuka, futsi ngitsandza kuhlale ngikhutsata bemitfombo yetindzaba.
Labanye batatisi baphikisana ngekutsi loku kucinisekiswa yini: Sanders akazange akhulume ne-White House Press kusukela ngaSeptemba 10.
Umhleli Chris Wallace wabuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders watsi bekungasiyo inkinga kutsi labamemeteli beTV bebangakhulumi kahle, kodvwa bekutsi "angikuphikisi kutsi bayakhuluma kabi".
