Kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye nematsunami e-Indonesia
Umhlaba watamatama kakhulu ngeLesihlanu, futsi ema-tsunami abulala bantfu labangu-384 ePalu, e-Indonesia, futsi tiphatsimandla titsi sibalo sebantfu labafile singakhuphuka.
Ngenca yekuhlukana kwetindlela tekuchumana, tisebenti tetinsita atikhoni kutfola lutfo lolumayelana neDongla Regency, lengasenyakatfo yePalu, lekungiyo lebeyinenhlitiyo yaloluhlupho lolubitwa ngekutsi ngu-7.5.
Bangetulu kwa-16 000 bantfu labahlala ePalu labaphutfuma etindzaweni letehlukene ngemuva kwenhlekelele.
Nati tintfo letibalulekile ePalu naseDongla eSulawesi:
I-Palu iyinhloko-dolobha yesifundza sase-Sulawesi Lesemkhatsini, lesiseceleni kwelwandle lolucinile lolusentshonalanga ye-Sulawesi Island, lebeyinebantfu labangu 379,800 nga-2017.
Ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami, lelidolobha beligubha iminyaka lengu-40 selishonile.
I-Dongla yi-regency leseceleni kwelugwini lolusenyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSulawesi, lengemakhilomitha langu-300 (emamayela langu-180).
Leligatja lifaka ekhatsi iRegency, indzawo yekuphatsa, lebeyinebantfu labangu 299,200 nga-2017.
Kudvweba nekulima kusisekelo semnotfo wesifundza sase-Central Sulawesi, ikakhulukati endzaweni yaseDongla.
Umsebenti wekucopha inhlaka ye-nickel nawo ubalulekile kulendzawo, kepha kuncono kutsi ugcizelele loku eMoro Valley, lephambene neSulawesi.
Ngekusho kwe-Indonesia Disaster Management Agency, ePalu naseDonggala sekube nema-tsunami lamanyenti kuleminyaka lengu-100 leyendlulile.
Nga-1938, ema-tsunami abulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi abhubhisa emakhaya lamanyenti.
Nga-1996, tsunami yahlasela emaveni langasenshonalanga yeDongla, yabulala bantfu labasiphohlongo.
INdonesia isendzaweni lenetindzawo letinemandla letisemkhatsini wePacific Ring of Fire futsi ivame kutfuswa kutamatama kwemhlaba.
Nati letinye tetindzawo letinemandla letinyakatako naletine-tsunami letenteka kuleminyaka lembalwa leyendlulile:
2004: NgaDecember 26, 2004, kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwenteka ngaselugwini lwasenshonalanga yeSifundza sase-Ache, lesiseNyakatfo yeSumatra, e-Indonesia, kwabangela kutsi kube nematsunami emaveni langu-14, kwabulala bantfu labangu-226,000, lokungacishe kube yincenye yabo lebebahlala e-Ache.
2005: Ngasekupheleni kwaMarch nasekucaleni kwa-April, kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokulandzelana lokwenteka entshonalanga neSumatra.
Bantfu labanyenti bafa esihlengeni saseNyashe lesingaselugwini lwaseSumatra.
2006: 2006: Umonakalo lobitwa ngekutsi yi-tsunami lenemandla lamakhulu kakhulu, yahlasela sihlenge lesiseningizimu ye-Indonesia, futsi yabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-700.
2009: Umhlaba watamatama kakhulu ngebubanti lobungu-7.6 edolobheni lasePadang, lelisesigodlweni saseWestern Sumatra.
Bangetulu kwa-1 100 bantfu labafa.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunebubanti lobungu-7.5 lokwenteka eMentawai Island eSumatra, kwabangela tsunami lephakeme ngemamitha langu-10 futsi kwabhubhisa emadolobha lamanyenti kwabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-300.
2016: P.D. Jaya Regency e-Achebe yatfukutsela kakhulu ngenca yekuhlaselwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabhubhisa lokunyenti futsi kwabangela kwesaba lokwakwenta kutsi kubhujiswe lokwakhumbuta bantfu ngekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami nga-2004.
Kute ema-tsunami labekhona, kodvwa kwafa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 ngenca yekubhidlika kwetakhiwo.
2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela sihlenge sase-Indonesia iLombok, kwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, labanyenti babo basenyakatfo yalesihlenge.
Tikhungo letinyenti tabhidlika futsi tinkhulungwane tetivakashi takhungatheka.
