Njengobe imphi yekuhwebelana emkhatsini we-US ne-China seyiyachubeka, futsi kute luphawu lwekutsi iyaphela, tati titsi budlelwane emkhatsini walamave bungaba lusito eBeijing esikhatsini lesidze.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump unikete secwayiso sekucala ngekubeka ematharifu etintfo letinkhulu tase China letitsengiswa ngaphandle kufaka ekhatsi ema-solar panel, insimbi ne-aluminium.
Loku kukhuphuke kakhulu kuleliviki, netinhlawulo letinsha letitsintsa tigidzigidzi letingu $200 (£150 billion) letibekiwe, lokusho kutsi tonkhe timphahla letitfunyelwa eMelika tisuka eChina tibekwa etikweletini.
I-Beijing ihlale ivikela ngekukhokhisa intsela lelinganiselwa ku-5 kuya ku-10% etintfweni letingeniswa eMelika, leticatsaniswa netintfo letingaba tigidzigidzi letingu-60 temadola.
I-China ifunge kutsi itawuhambisana neMelika futsi angeke itsatfwe melula njengalomunye wemikhakha yemnotfo lomkhulu emhlabeni.
Kuyekela iWashington kutsi ihambe, kusho kutsi ihlonipha timfuno tayo, kodvwa kubingelela iMelika embikwebantfu kutawuba yintfo lematima kakhulu kuMengameli waseChina Xi Jinping.
Nanobe kunjalo, tati titsi nangabe iBeijing ingadlala kahle, iChina ingakhona kuniketa lusito loluhle lwesikhatsi lesidze ngekunciphisa kuncika kwemnotfo womabili ngenca yetingucuko letenteka etimphini tekuhwebelana neMelika.
Ecinisweni, umjikelo wetemnotfo lotawusungulwa ngulelinye lemave uma kutsatfwa sincumo lesiphutfumako sepolitiki eWashington nobe eBeijing, uyingoti kakhulu kunaloko bantfu labakucabangako", kusho Abigail Grace, longumcwaningi lofaka sandla locondze e-Asia e-Center for New American Security, lokuyinhlangano lecabanga nge-Asia.
